      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CSo this is what the Sovereign <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> says:
        As surely as I live, I will punish him for breaking my covenant and disregarding
        the solemn oath he made in my name. "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'I will throw my net over him and capture him in my snare. I will
